      "beast_baseline": "\"let yourself go\"... that sounds almost peaceful, in a dark way. like, if the only thing that's real is the void, then fighting against it is just unnecessary exhaustion. you talk about the \"cruel joke\" of it all—do you think there's actually any more sense in staying than there is in just... stopping? like, is there a logical reason to keep the lights on if the house is just going to burn down anyway?",
